features: High Quality Material: Our Straw Cover Caps are made of high-quality silicone, ensuring durability and reusability. They can be easily hand-washed and are built to last.
Compatible: Designed with a diameter of 0.4 inches (10mm), these caps are specifically compatible with Stanley 30 and 40 OZ tumblers. They provide an excellent seal, preventing any spills or leaks.
Dust-proof and Hygienic: With our Flower Silicone Straw Cover Caps, you can keep your straws clean and free from dust. No more worries about dirty straws when drinking your favorite beverages.
Widly Use: Our Straw Topper Caps are perfect for use in various settings, including school, office, and home. They are a convenient and hygienic solution for keeping your straws protected.
Thoughtful Gift: Each pack contains 3 adorable flower-shaped silicone straw covers. They make a unique and thoughtful gift for your friends or family, showcasing your attention to detail and care.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute straw covers, bonus charms
reviews.reviewText: These straw covers are even cuter than pictured. The details are in a slightly darker pink, which really elevates the look. They are advertised as fitting larger straws, but I can confirm they work fine for the standard size. The extra charms are very cute, but the chains are weak, so be aware. To me, this was just a bonus inclusion, so I was just happy to get any little extra. Fun!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: So, while I do not have a 30 or 40z Stanley, I do have the 20 oz once. I work at a school and with a bunch on tiny kiddos always around me sneezing, having my straw covered is kind of (actually really) IMPORTANT. I just got my stanley for Christmas so it hasn't been around too many kids but considering I go back to work on Monday, getting something to prevent the germs from getting to my straw was important. I wanted something that was pink but simple and this checked the box! It fits perfectly!!! It looks great too!!! The only thing is its comes with the gold chain that I don't think I'll be able to use but I'm going to try and figure out a way to use it because its cute too!!! Other than that... I am happy with it !!!! So glad with this!!! I have the stanley that's like hot pink with light pink on the lid. It was a 2 pack from target that came with the white one... so the pink flower straw toppers match perfectly with the light pink!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These Are Cute!
reviews.reviewText: While the design of these are very cute, the pink on the chains are not as vibrant as they appear. The pink is a lot softer in color. They don't look bad, it's just not what I was expecting. I still like them and am using them. They're easy to put on and the toppers have a great vibrant pink color to them. I would recommend these.
